title: What time does Strictly Come Dancing start?
text:
What time does Strictly Come Dancing start? By WMNdellis | Posted: October 10, 2015 9237159-low_res-strictly-come-dancing-2015 What time does Strictly Come Dancing start? X 
Copy link to paste in your message / Comments (0) 
There will be sequins and sparkle galore on tonight's Strictly, when the contestants dance their way through this week's movie-themed show. 
Judges Len Goodman, Bruno Tonioli, Craig Revel Horwood and Darcey Bussell will of course be on hand to give advice and criticism. 
Tess Daly and Claudia Winkleman present the show. 
It starts at 6.20pm
